ed="T" n="0796a23"/><persName key="A001434">釋愛同</persName>，俗姓<name>趙</name>氏，本<placeName key="PL000000044976">天水</placeName>人也。代襲冠冕<lb
ed="T" n="0796a24"/>弱齡挺拔，惠然肯來<ptr type="glossary" target="#g389"/>，為佛家子。具戒後，講彌<lb
ed="T" n="0796a25"/>沙塞律<ptr target="#n1514"/>，遠近師稟，若鱗羽宗乎鯤鳳<ptr target="#n1027"/>也。昔<lb
ed="T" n="0796a26"/>南<date from-iso="+0420-07-11" key="j18746541896160" to-iso="+0479-05-29"><name>宋</name></date>朝<placeName key="PL000000055418">罽賓</placeName>三藏<persName key="A000436">覺壽</persName>譯成此律，因出《羯磨》<ptr type="glossary" target="#g390"/><lb
ed="T" n="0796a27"/>一卷，時運遷移，其本零落，尋求不獲，學者無<lb
ed="T" n="0796a28"/>依。<persName key="A001434">同</persName>遂於大律之內，抄出《羯磨》一卷<ptr target="#n1030"/>，彼宗<lb
ed="T" n="0796a29"/>學者盛傳流布，被事方全。<persName key="A002100">孝和</persName>之世，<date notBefore-iso="+0705-02-25" key="j19786111979566" notAfter-iso="+0707-10-08"><name>神龍</name>中</date><pb ed="T" n="0796b" xml:id="T50.2061.0796b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0796b01"/>盛重翻宣，<persName key="A001434">同</persName>與<persName key="A002468">文綱</persName>等參預譯場，推為證<lb
ed="T" n="0796b02"/>義。<persName key="A001470">義淨</persName>所出之經，<persName key="A001434">同</persName>有力焉。著《五分律疏》<lb
ed="T" n="0796b03"/>十卷，復遺囑<placeName key="PL000000042216">西明寺</placeName><persName key="A010850">玄通<roleName>律師</roleName></persName>重施潤色。<lb
ed="T" n="0796b04"/>後<persName key="A008454">安</persName><persName key="A010333">史</persName><ptr target="#n382"/>俶擾<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1048"/>，焚燎喪寺，今無類矣。</p>
